I2C

https://microdigisoft.com/esp8266-nodemcu-i2c-communication/
Typical values for 5V devices are 4.7k Ohm and 2.4k Ohm for 3.3V devices.

https://forum.arduino.cc/t/i2c-communication-between-nodemcu-and-arduino-uno/534715/6
1500 ohm to 3.3

https://forum.arduino.cc/t/i2c-bus-with-3-3v-and-5-0v-device/113914/4
I hooked up 4.7k resistors between I2C lines and +3.3 volts and it works great.